SubjectAmendment to the Teslin Tlingit Council Self-Government Agreement
PrecisOrder Amending the TESLIN TLINGIT COUNCIL SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to delete sections 13.6.3, 13.6.4, 13.6.5, 13.6.6 and 13.6.7 and replace them with new sections 13.6.3, 13.6.4 and 13.6.5. The purpose of this amendment is to bring into effect the Teslin Tlingit Council Administration of Justice Agreement and incorporate it into the Teslin Tlingit Council Self-Government Agreement.
